Interface ExifTags.Pentax

  • Enclosing interface:
    ExifTags
    public static interface ExifTags.Pentax
    Definition of specialized Pentax Exif tags.

    For further descriptions, tags see http://www.exif.org/Exif2-2.PDF or the manufacturer definitions.

    Since:
    5.0.100
